---
slug: "contact"
permalink: "/es/contact/index.html"
title: "Request a transfer | Morrison Premium Transfer"
description: "Brief to confirm a transfer: route, date, passengers, contact. One minute to fill."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Inicio", path: "/es/" }
  - { name: "Contact", path: "/es/contact/" }
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="kicker">{{ t.brief.title }}</p>
    <h1>Every trip starts with a brief.</h1>
    <p class="lead">{{ t.brief.subtitle }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    {% include "partials/brief-form.njk" %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--bg-soft">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="kicker">Contact channels</p>
    <h2>Reach us where it's easiest for you.</h2>
    <div class="contact-channels">
      <a class="contact-channel" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="eyebrow">Fastest</span>
        <span class="contact-channel-name">WhatsApp</span>
        <span class="contact-channel-detail">Reply usually within an hour in business hours. Voice notes welcome too.</span>
      </a>
      <a class="contact-channel" href="{{ site.contacts.telegramUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="eyebrow">More relaxed</span>
        <span class="contact-channel-name">Telegram</span>
        <span class="contact-channel-detail">Great for long routes and exchanging documents before the trip.</span>
      </a>
      <a class="contact-channel" href="mailto:{{ site.contacts.email }}">
        <span class="eyebrow">Written</span>
        <span class="contact-channel-name">Email</span>
        <span class="contact-channel-detail">For corporate correspondence, NF-e and cases with attachments.</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2>Urgent?</h2>
    <div class="cta-strip-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp now</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ site.contacts.telegramUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Telegram</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
